# [`mmrrc`](https://bioregistry.io/mmrrc): Mutant Mouse Resource and Research Centers

This page summarize the different resources that reference `mmrrc`
but use local unique identifiers that do not match the standard pattern of
`^\d+$`. Of the 1 resources,
1 variants on the standard prefix were found: ['MMRRC'].
